1. Declares the complaints concerning the conditions of the applicant s pretrial detention and the lack of an effective domestic remedy in that regard admissible and the remainder of the application inadmissible;
2. Holds that there has been no violation of Article 3 of the Convention;
3. Holds that there has been a violation of Article 13 of the Convention;
